title: We Love Muzik
description: We love Muzik (WLM) is a group of two young talented Burundian Artists; Dj Fernando and Gusto Kuriyo whom are signed under db Music Entertainment to help them push their work further. WLM started their music journey back in 2019 where they were able to release few songs. In 2020 in December, they released a hit song called "MOLO" that brought attention from all over the world due to the smoothness and well produced of the masterpiece. From there, they have been rising to the level that no one expected. Since then they have released songs like " LIKE YOU", "AWAY" and now their recent work is their first EP called "MALO" which includes 5 total songs. The goals of this group is to promote their lovely country and culture all around the world through their art of music. With the help of each one of you who are reading this, YES WE CAN. For support reach out: muzikwelove@gmail.com

title: D-ONE
description:
Dieudonne Ndayikengurukiye (born 15 May 1996), better known by his stage name D-ONE is a Burundian singer, and songwriter who is currently signed to ITEKA MUSIC Management in Burundi. 

 In 2021, D-ONE emerged in the spotlight with his debut song "Waiting", which introduced him to the world. Later on, he has released many more songs including "Body" featuring Social Mula" which grabbed different charts In Burundi and Rwanda and some other part of the world. 

D-ONE managed to grab a very deserving AWARDS as the best upcoming artist of the year in 2021, till then he hasn't stopped  releasing hit after hit which makes him one of most trending artist in the country.

title: Sat-B
description: Sat-B is a Burundian singer/songwriter who started his solo career in 2009 after breaking off from his former music group Wanavesi Kikosi. His solo career led him to his stardom and massive success in Burundi. He made his big break 2010 with the single Inkuru y'Ukuri and since then he has consistently delivered hit after hit. With a career spanning a decade, he has risen to become one of Burundi‚Äôs biggest stars in R&B and Hip-Hop and ready to conquer Africa. He continues to collaborate with different artists in the region.

title: Victorious Team
description:
"Victorious Team" is a christian gospel hiphop group, based in Burundi, composed by multiple authors, compositors and singers of many different urban styles of music, under the anointing for the work of the Prophet Evrard Sinagaye(TRM church).
"We preach the Truth revealed: Jesus dead on the cross for our redemption."
In activity since 2016, "Victorious Team" has been delivering its best works on Youtube and all medias of the country (and outside) for a pure entertainment and gospel teaching purpose. 
For any question, contact us on our email: victoriousteam16@gmail.com
Or welcome to our work place: TRM church(Truth Revealed Ministry).
